query:
SELECT 
  at.id as auditTypeId,
  at.auditName,
  atem.id as templateId,
  atem.templateName,
  atem.isActive,
  atem.auditTypeId as templateAuditTypeId
FROM auditTypes at
LEFT JOIN auditTemplates atem ON at.id = atem.auditTypeId
WHERE at.id IN (SELECT DISTINCT auditTypeId FROM auditInstances WHERE auditTemplateId IS NULL)
LIMIT 10;
